            <thetext>The problem can be shown easily be an example:


&quot;decA&quot; :
{
  style :
  {
     radius : 10
  }
},

&quot;decB&quot; :
{
  include &quot;decA&quot;,
  style :
  {
     radiusBottomLeft : 0
  }
}


This example can result in that way, widgets with &quot;decB&quot; will be set to a radius of 10px to all four corners. We should handle that issue.

One way could be to automatically transform group properties to their parts before merging the style maps.</thetext>
